@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@next "Requirements"
@prev "Distribution and Legal Stuff"
@{u}Introduction@{uu}

 @{b}SelectCookie@{ub} is a selector [surprise!,surprise! 8)] for Cookies, 
used as Goodies in EMails. The main difference to the other available 
cookie-selecting programms [Hi Quip, Hi AmigaETag ! :)] is its speed on 
selecting a cookie. Well to be honest, you can`t select a cookie ?! (but
if you could, I would take all the chocolate ones :) )
@{b}SelectCookie@{ub} jumps randomized somewhere into your Cookiefile, 
walks a bit around until the next cookie is found, and then reads it 
aloud to the audience.
@endnode

